title: Elon Musk's X Sues Nonprofit That Accused It of Allowing Hate Speech

title: X Sign Removed From Top of Former Twitter HQ
description: The X sign, erected on Friday atop the company’s building in downtown San Francisco, was removed after two dozen complaints from residents and a city citation.
